rawIntent:
[Feature: Build the leave management module — Phase 1: Define leave domain models and repository layer]

Create src/modules/leave/leave.model.ts defining the canonical LeaveRequest entity shape and DTOs used by persistence (including fields id, employeeId, leaveType, startDate, endDate, status, approverEmployeeId, createdAt). Create src/modules/leave/leave.repository.ts implementing the leave persistence contract and repository methods that operate on LeaveRequest types from src/modules/leave/leave.model.ts. Create tests/unit/modules/leave/leave.repository.spec.ts covering repository behavior and type usage. Keep all LeaveRequest type definitions and repository code in this phase so the repository references the actual model file.

